uspected-stabbing-attack-south-of-jerusalem-assailant-shot/0000018c-b1ea-d45c-a98e-bbeeb3070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在中部城市罗德刺死幼童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-stabs-toddler-to-death-in-central-city-of-lod/0000018c-b1a1-d014-a3cd-bbbf8e200000</link><description>警方认为嫌疑人患有精神疾病；男孩的母亲说，这名男子不知从哪里突然跳出来，在没有任何挑衅的情况下刺伤了她在婴儿车里的儿子，也没有试图伤害她</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 18:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-stabs-toddler-to-death-in-central-city-of-lod/0000018c-b1a1-d014-a3cd-bbbf8e200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，内塔尼亚胡的司法政变卷土重来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-28/ty-article/.highlight/with-israel-at-war-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-with-a-vengeance/0000018c-b146-d45c-a98e-bb4e59d20000</link><description>原本的司法改革计划可能会被搁置，但政府还有更危险的空间，可以不受限制和不被注意地扩大权力。公众心烦意乱，忙着恐慌或聚集在旗帜周围</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 18:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-28/ty-article/.highlight/with-israel-at-war-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-with-a-vengeance/0000018c-b146-d45c-a98e-bb4e59d20000</guid></item><item><title>不负责任地使用抗菌药物构成健康威胁，而不是加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2023-12-28/ty-article/irresponsible-use-of-antimicrobials-poses-a-health-threat-not-gaza/0000018c-b0f2-d45c-a98e-bbfe6e350000</link><description>对以色列士兵可能在加沙感染耐药疾病并将其传播给以色列普通民众的担忧基本上是没有根据的，特别是考虑到更大的担忧——无论加沙在世界范围内，耐药感染一直在上升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 17:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2023-12-28/ty-article/irresponsible-use-of-antimicrobials-poses-a-health-threat-not-gaza/0000018c-b0f2-d45c-a98e-bbfe6e350000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列历史上最糟糕的一年——但现在还不是绝望的时候</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-the-worst-year-in-israels-history-but-now-is-not-the-time-to-despair/0000018c-b0cd-db94-afbd-b0fd936d0000</link><description>这一年发生了可怕的事件——弥赛亚政府、司法政变和哈马斯大屠杀——使今年成为“内塔尼亚胡年”。然而，尽管情况很糟糕，以色列仍有时间在 2024 年改变路线</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-the-worst-year-in-israels-history-but-now-is-not-the-time-to-despair/0000018c-b0cd-db94-afbd-b0fd936d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列应该考虑对黎巴嫩进行地面入侵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lebanon-cant-control-hezbollah-israel-must-broaden-military-action/0000018c-af85-db94-afbd-affdcae40000</link><description>真主党与哈马斯一样致力于摧毁以色列和实施 10 月 7 日式的暴行，但更具杀伤力。其不断增加的导弹和无人机袭击以及黎巴嫩的消极态度证明以色列有理由进行广泛的自卫报复</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:40:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lebanon-cant-control-hezbollah-israel-must-broaden-military-action/0000018c-af85-db94-afbd-affdcae40000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔任命新以色列监狱管理局局长，违反战时政府条款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-appoints-new-israel-prison-service-chief-violating-terms-of-wartime-government/0000018c-b0fd-db94-afbd-b0fd39330000</link><description>目前尚不清楚国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔是否有权任命目前担任其安全顾问的科比·雅科比少将，或者是否需要政府做出决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:38:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-appoints-new-israel-prison-service-chief-violating-terms-of-wartime-government/0000018c-b0fd-db94-afbd-b0fd39330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国人朱迪·韦恩斯坦·哈盖 (Judi Weinstein Haggai) 于 10 月 7 日被谋杀，据信被哈马斯绑架</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-judi-weinstein-haggai-believed-kidnapped-by-hamas-was-murdered-on-oct-7/0000018c-b120-d014-a3cd-bb3ece670000</link><description>10 月 7 日早上，