-the-developed-world-new-report-shows/0000018c-b055-d45c-a98e-bb5d02af0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫高中校长因同情加沙人的苦难而面临停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</link><description>校长因在她的 Facebook 页面上发布《国土报》的一篇文章而被传唤参加听证会，该文章批评以色列媒体对加沙人道主义危机缺乏报道</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定，国家不能歧视想要收养的同性伴侣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-cant-discriminate-against-same-sex-couples-looking-to-adopt-top-court-rules/0000018c-b0d2-d014-a3cd-bade63a80000</link><description>高等法院裁定，在收养孩子的过程中，异性恋不应优先于同性伴侣</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-cant-discriminate-against-same-sex-couples-looking-to-adopt-top-court-rules/0000018c-b0d2-d014-a3cd-bade63a80000</guid></item><item><title>纳粹掠夺了她的艺术品。 10月7日，哈马斯又偷走了另一件雕塑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/museums-exhibits/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-nazis-looted-her-sculpture-on-october-7-hamas-stole-another-piece/0000018c-afbb-d45c-a98e-afffd7710000</link><description>80 年前被纳粹掠夺的一位法国犹太先驱艺术家的作品究竟属于一位来自伦敦的犹太妇女还是该艺术家的孙女？这件事和10月7日的事件有什么关系呢？</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/museums-exhibits/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-nazis-looted-her-sculpture-on-october-7-hamas-stole-another-piece/0000018c-afbb-d45c-a98e-afffd7710000</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告对西岸权利“迅速恶化”表示遗憾</title><link>https://www.